          ],
          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "When the hunter dies, their soul leaves their body in an explosion of spiritual energy. All creatures in a 20-foot burst take 5d6 spirit damage (DC 19 basic Will save). The hunter's possessions are left in a pile where they died.",
