              "name": "Two Actions",
              "subtype": "action_type",
              "type": "stat_block_section"
            },
            "name": "Double Slice",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The caligni hunter makes two Strikes against the same target, one with each of their shortswords. The hunter combines the damage of any attacks that hit and applies precision damage, resistances, and weaknesses only once. Both attacks count toward the hunter's multiple attack penalty, but the penalty increases only after both attacks.",
            "type": "stat_block_section"
          },
          "name": "Double Slice",
          "offensive_action_type": "ability",
          "subtype": "offensive_action",
          "type": "stat_block_section"
        },
        {
